Genevieve Townsend https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genevieve_Townsend 0 Genevieve Townsend (December 4, 1897 – May 1, 1927) was an American stage and film actress. She was born in the United States, but later moved to Britain. In the mid-1920s she had several lead roles in British silent films. She died in Switzerland at the age of 29 in 1927.
